{"tid":622610,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好鍾意九十年代既香港娛圈","createTime":"2018-04-09T09:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T08:59:23.000Z","uid":82917,"like":46,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"82d6b97d56dc0b26e9569664c11de89235becd04","tid":622610,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:18:28.000Z","msg":"雖然唔係生係呢個年代，但由細細個睇古惑仔開始，就好想自己出世係個個年代。。。想感受個陣既香港<br />\n97之前既香港。。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個陣既香港真係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前既黑社會真係好撚恐怖，仲有街童。。<br />\n而家變到黑警渣正牌做爛仔，呢個社會真係到有黑有白先平權到。<br />\n三五成群睇幾多次都係會好撚唔舒服。<br />\n成日ff自己如果俾同童蝦收保護費會點，報警都冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該嚇到尿滲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n明星又係，個陣時既佢地先叫明星<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十幾廿年姐，點解會退步到咁？？<br />\n九十年代既女星真係位位都索撚到仆街！！！<br />\n西女人，豆豆，細細粒，姐姐，maggie，王祖賢，紅姑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講極都有，真係行出黎就係天生明星，注定食呢行飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個都靚得好有特色，2000年後已經出唔到呢挺美人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯一諗到已經係karena<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢地好多都好早就結婚息影。。。<br />\n好想感受佢地當紅既時代，百花齊放既娛樂圈<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再講返，千禧年代既明星都開始唔係好撚掂，好似全部都被係人恥笑多過讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇乜邊幾個隔左十幾年後都名留青史<br />\n（例如edc, lemon, fisherman, twins, 春卷, 單春）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好想生係80年代去感受90年代既輝煌啊啊啊啊<br />\n<br />\n身邊個個都笑我老餅，鍾意睇老餅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我覺得呢個年代先叫香港，回不去的香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我仲好鍾意睇溏心風暴同真情，雖然溏心係07-08年，但個種人情味，已經再也不可能係電視上睇到了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點拍都拍唔出個種味道了。。。<br />\n一家團聚食餐飯，唱下鳩叫中秋玩下燈籠又一年，真係好幸福。<br />\n笑聲笑聲，滿載溫馨，快樂發心內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解我唔早廿年出世？"},{"pid":"81aff6255d526c4cfaf79d552beb974f78ef7e18","tid":622610,"uid":82917,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:21:51.000Z","msg":"長文叫春<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個陣啲八掛仲好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如眾所周知既<br />\n大瘤 西女人<br />\n關小姐 高爾夫球<br />\n肥蛆 美玲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n春卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n+0 神童輝<br />\n撚太撚 小小超<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有好多好多一時醒唔起，間唔時就走去搵舊娛聞睇黎。真係好撚黑暗又好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a182b3ce5f3528f09a3e3528b41708b66aee92fc","tid":622610,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:22:21.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以爆啲舊時既娛聞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e47e386594a5cd6d40c071e507eca3b09ab13347","tid":622610,"uid":82917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:29:33.000Z","msg":"Ok...又得我懷念過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"382e448451957736acdd03cab2332f1722511b20","tid":622610,"uid":82917,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:30:16.000Z","msg":"同親身邊啲人講，一係就「唔識喎」「邊個黎」<br />\n完全傾唔到計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就黎要同呀媽傾呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b3651620372fc041334fb8ef53a73d498cc732","tid":622610,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:57:16.000Z","msg":"即到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e569df323ec989bfb2c5bae3ced8d388c4d7b0d","tid":622610,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:57:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d12